        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong></strong><b>Freedom to Invest in a Sustainable Future Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for fiduciaries of employer-sponsored retirement plans to consider environmental, social, governance, or similar factors when making investment decisions.</p>]]></text>
